Class SharepointSession

com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.Session
public class SharepointSession
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.Session

Implements the Session interface from the spi. It implements methods to return AuthenticationManager, AuthorizationManager and the QueryTraversalManager for the Sharepoint connector to the caller.
